name: Riae
description:
Riae (born September 24, 1984) is an Italian model who is best recognized for her alternative modeling style and for having earned representation from the Suicide Girls modeling agency. She shares additional modeling photos through her Instagram as well for her over 4.5 million followers. 

If you like my work, a review is more than welcome! Also, follow me on Twitter or Instagram!

Looking for something... spicy? Here's my Patreon!

Also, I recently started a blog where I will gather resources and tutorials about my work here!

Hello, nice people of Civitai! Today I present to you my textual inversion of Riae! I used 50 images of her (30 close portraits, 20 half-lenght), with a 9000 steps process. To use it in your works:

  • download the file and place it into stable-diffusion-webui>embeddings folder;

  • add riae84 to your prompt;

  • keep the sampling steps around 30, and CFG between 6 and 8 to work well. Great results with DPM++ SDE Karras & Realistic Vision. Face restore could help sometimes, to make some softer lines when necessary;

meta.prompt: RAW photo, a close-up photo of riae84 wearing a black sweater, (high detailed skin:1.2), 8k UHD, DSLR, soft lighting, high quality, film grain, Fujifilm XT3
